NAME
    App::LogGerUtils - Command-line utilities related to Log::ger

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.002 of App::LogGerUtils (from Perl
    distribution App-LogGerUtils), released on 2017-08-03.

SYNOPSIS
    This distribution provides the following command-line utilities related
    to Log::ger:

    *   log-ger-demo-screen-colors

    *   log-ger-demo-screen-colors-with-levels-like-logany

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/App-LogGerUtils>.

SOURCE
    Source repository is at
    <https://github.com/perlancar/perl-App-LogGerUtils>.

BUGS
    Please report any bugs or feature requests on the bugtracker website
    <https://rt.cpan.org/Public/Dist/Display.html?Name=App-LogGerUtils>

    When submitting a bug or request, please include a test-file or a patch
    to an existing test-file that illustrates the bug or desired feature.

